{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act43side", "eventName": "紅絲絨", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "AD-6", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "倒帶獨白", "storyInfo": "格蕾塔意識到盧西恩的眼光不僅聚焦於戲中，更投向戲外，她正式邀請盧西恩成為“主角”，解決地塊上發生的事件。而盧西恩做的第一步，就是揪出連環兇案的兇手——莫伊拉。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_lungmencommand", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_energywell", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "en"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.8, "channel": "en", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "漆黑一片的樓層裡，身形嬌小的札拉克女孩獨自摸索著。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$2", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……原來如此。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$2"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然構造和系統看起來很複雜，但只要搞清楚原理……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$2"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$2"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算是小小的道具師也能操作。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$2"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比如這裡，先調整一下方向……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$2"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_keyboard_console", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "key"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "key", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$2"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "設定好時間，將拉杆往下拉，打開閘口，然後……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$2"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "成功了。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$2"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#10$2"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，跟我想的完全一樣。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#10$2"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣一來就算發生意料之外的事情……也不用擔心了。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#10$2"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，只剩下最後一件事……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$2"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要去找她。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$2"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "en", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g10_dormitory", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道你有顧慮，盧西恩。", "name": "格蕾塔"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在地塊上危機重重，人人自危，一個不顧一切並放狠話要繼續拍攝的製片人，怎麼看都不是值得信任的對象。", "name": "格蕾塔"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們之間無需信任。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵……沒錯。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#7$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在藍卡塢從業二十年，我從來沒有信任過任何合作夥伴，我相信的只有自己的眼光。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在米蘭妮最需要機會的時候發出邀約，我在拍賣會上一眼看出你是演戲奇才，我咬定阿布納恨我但還是會加入劇組。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我還確信五年前勞拉之死是挽救電影的唯一解答。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你與那起意外並無關聯，但你利用了她的死。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "勞拉是個有天分的新人。她好學、勤奮、對電影充滿熱情，只是有時候積極過頭，破壞了一些規矩。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當時斯蒂芬經驗淺薄，拍攝並沒有達到預期的效果。拍攝進行到中途，我就意識到這部電影一定會掏空我的資產，甚至葬送我的聲譽。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我需要“場外因素”幫我渡過這次危機……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "勞拉的墜亡。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "用媒體炒作片場故事缺乏意義，好事者只會唏噓幾句，轉頭就會遺忘。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我花重金壓下了警方的調查和電視台對此事的關注，給勞拉的家人一筆可觀的撫恤金……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓剪輯師完整保留了阿布納拍攝的墜亡片段，故意製作成劇中的一幕高潮……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到現在還有人認為她是早早息影的天才演員……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你隱瞞了她的死。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我讓她在電影中永生。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總有人會注意到你的手段。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每年勞拉的祭日，我都會去看望她。五年過去，她的墓前只有我為她帶的花。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#7$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你毫不愧疚？", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我難辭其咎。但懺悔，不是現在。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "此時此刻我最想做的只有一件事——把電影拍完。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等《杜邦夫人之死》上映後，拍攝中發生的幾起命案勢必會引來媒體的關注，我也會藉此正式公開勞拉死亡的真相。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到時候會有更多人為她悼念，而我將承擔我應有的罪責。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#3$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你應該明白，我剛剛的坦承並非只是有感而發。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#8$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想用自己的真相跟我交易。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遇見你之初我還以為是命運的垂青，為我即將開拍的電影送來一份大禮。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而你進組後的種種表現，讓我確認你的身分異於常人。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老道爾頓死在你的面前，你神情鎮定，甚至還期待之後的拍攝。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "找到我打算拍攝天災的線索之後，你將它在絕妙的時機分享給最會傳播消息的攝影助理。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，劇組正式解散，幾乎所有人都陷入絕境，而你卻在房間內等待我的拜訪，彷彿早已習慣突如其來的悲劇和死亡。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你到底是誰？你到底為什麼答應加入劇組？", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是被你拍下的劇本吸引，沒有其他原因。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許吧。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#7$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事到如今盤問你的來歷也無助於我的拍攝，但我希望我的坦誠也能換來你的坦誠。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩先生，我相信自己的眼光，就算我在你身上發現了無數可疑之處，我依然不會收回讓你擔任主角的邀請。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是——", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你無法明說真正的目的，如果你的視角遠高於我……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你認為勞拉之死，以及五年後由此引發的一切，才是這個地塊上真正在拍攝的“故事”，而你正是為此而來……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格蕾塔·斯通願意再一次向你發出邀請……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去成為接下來的“主角”吧，盧西恩先生。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如你所願……如我所願，格蕾塔女士。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#11$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.2, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.2, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_darkforest", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“……格蕾塔……清點並發放所有人的酬勞，正式解散了整個劇組……”", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“畏懼兇手的、忌憚天災的、堅持拍攝的……都可以任意決定自己的去留，各行其是。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "堅持拍攝？格蕾塔到現在還想著自己的電影？", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她不可能猜不到劇組的兇案與五年前的命案有關。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "所以，她是故意的……", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstpwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“深層原因？在這種情況下難道還有人想要追尋真相嗎？”", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“或者，按照格蕾塔的說法——把真相交給想當偵探的好事者吧。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "真相？", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "劇組成員明目張膽欺凌新人，製片人還將墜亡的悲劇包裝成似真似假的戲。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "既不為五年前的事懺悔，也不將自己的所作所為公之於眾……", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "格蕾塔，難道你自認為是無辜的嗎？難道你忘了被你剪到電影裡一遍遍死去的勞拉了嗎？", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你必須付出代價。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_open_door", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"type": "bg", "id": "62_g10_dormitory", "from": 0.0, "to": 0.5, "duration": 0.1, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g10_dormitory", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wtchkgopenftstp", "volume": 0.8, "loop": "true", "channel": "wt"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "wt", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"type": "bg", "id": "62_g10_dormitory", "from": 0.5, "to": 0.0, "duration": 3.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.1, "yFrom": 0.0, "yTo": 50.0, "duration": 3.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "藉著夜燈微弱的光，隱約能看到床上的隆起。蒙在被中的人還在安穩的睡夢中，對審判的到來一無所知。"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安穩？羞辱逝者，遺忘罪孽，無視警告……格蕾塔憑什麼能睡得安穩？"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drawsword", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個人悄無聲息地接近床頭，衣袖滑出一把鋒利的匕首。纖細的手指死死抓住刀柄，將兇器高高舉起。"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "連懺悔都不想聽到，連哀鳴都覺得刺耳，就這樣消失吧！付出代價吧！"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "r"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "r", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 1.3, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleTo": 1.3, "duration": 0.8, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.8, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 90.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_knife", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g10_dormitory", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "觸感不對……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "channel": "e", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.7, "bend": 1.0, "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "將被子一把掀開，裡面空無一人，只有黑色的影子。"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "影子？影子怎麼會憑空出現？"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來人向後退了幾步，影子慢慢凝聚成了熟悉的樣子。"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_meowlong", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_catfootstep", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#2$1", "duration": 0.2}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cakebgflgrnd", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……Miss.Christine？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4198_christ_1#2$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陷阱……", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4198_christ_1#2$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spotlight", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodfloor_fts", "volume": 0.5, "loop": "true", "channel": "sn"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "sn", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "終於見面了。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歡迎你，神出鬼沒的客人。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#11$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#3$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的是……你？", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#3$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_sys_rglk1phantomcastle_intro", "key": "$m_sys_rglk1phantomcastle_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$2", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$2"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫伊拉……劇組裡最敬業的成員，你真的是三起命案的兇手……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#3$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$2"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本來應該是四起。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$2"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$2"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩先生，你是什麼時候發現的？", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$2"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最先發現你的反常之處的不是我，是Miss.Christine。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我進組的第一場戲，Miss.Christine闖入拍攝現場。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除了我之外，她一般不會主動靠近別人，但她接近你了。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從那以後，她與你接觸了很多次。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂比認為Miss.Christine特地跑到道具間陪你們一起看電影是因為喜歡你們……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這句話有一半是對的。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Miss.Christine只是對你感興趣。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看現在……儘管你手裡還握著兇器，她還是在你身邊。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$2", "posfrom": "-100,0", "posto": "-100,0", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#3$2", "posfrom": "-100,0", "posto": "0,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "！", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#3$2"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#7$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "荒唐……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#7$2"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道你就憑這隻神秘生物的喜好來推測兇手嗎！", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#7$2"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#13$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是說作為你的寵物，她奉行的是你的意旨……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#13$2"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫伊拉對上Miss.Christine深邃的藍眼睛。"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下一秒，她的意識不再受自己支配。"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喜悅、悲傷、憤怒，種種情緒在心中翻湧，最終變為一片空白，空虛得令人恐懼。"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你對Miss.Christine依舊有些誤解。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#13$2"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我曾解釋過，沒人能干涉Miss.Christine的意願與行動。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#13$2"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這句話的意思，並不是指Miss.Christine天性自由，而是指沒有人“有能力”干涉她。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#13$2"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她才是“有能力”左右他人的那一個。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#13$2"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_meowlong", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "神秘的黑色生物若無其事地舔著爪子。"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫伊拉很難將現在的Miss.Christine與剛剛自己所受的巨大壓力聯想在一起。"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Miss.Christine對情緒感知十分敏銳——強行掩飾的痛苦、轉瞬即逝的邪念……都會引起她的注意。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#13$2"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在漫長的時間裡，她走遍泰拉的各個角落，品嚐過萬千的喜怒哀樂……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#13$2"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比起某種單一的情感，Miss.Christine更偏愛雜糅的情緒。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#13$2"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的判斷基於本能而非邏輯，絕無可能出錯。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#13$2"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在沒有發現任何作案動機的情況下破解了兇案……盧西恩先生，我應該恭喜你嗎？", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#13$2"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "復仇。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#3$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#13$2"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#13$2"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為誰？", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#13$2"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為纏繞在劇組大多數人心中的那個幽靈。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#4$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格蕾塔女士，現在站在你面前的是五年前墜亡的新人演員勞拉的親人——", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深愛著她的，妹妹。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}